Class DFSCollector

              org.jscripter.emu.gc.DFSCollector

public final class DFSCollector
extends DFS

An internal class for DOM-enabled depth-first-search garbage collectors emulating garbage collection based finalization in JavaScript.

This class is only used internally by JS re-compiler implementations.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
JavaScript:
This class is only loaded and resolved by re-compiler implementations.
